Package: egonet
Type: Package
Title: A small tool for Social Network Analysis, dealing with egocentric network measures, 
  including Burt's effective size and aggregate constraint and an import code suitable for a large number of adjacency matrices.
Version: 1.2
Date: 2018-10-17
Author: (Andrea Sciandra, Livio Finos).
Maintainer: livio finos <livio@stat.unipd.it>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    sna
Description: A small tool for Social Network Analysis, dealing with egocentric network measures, 
  including Burt's effective size and aggregate constraint and an import code suitable for a large number of adjacency matrices.
License: GPL (>= 2)
